
# Event_booking_System

# Run project Command :- 
-- npm run dev
   node index.js

##############################################  FILE AND FOLDER STRCTURE  ###########################################################################################################################################################################################################

 
├── index.js                     # Main application entry point , Main file
├── controllers/                  # Code for handling API endpoint logic
│   ├── authController.js         # User registration and login logic with the help of jwt toekn
│   └── eventsController.js       # Event CRUD and booking logic here 
├── middlewares/                  # Middleware folder
│   ├── middleware.js             # JWT middleware and organizer role check here
├── models/ 
    ├── users.js                  # Scehma / Model for users 
    ├── events_m.js               # Scehma / Model for create events 
    ├── eventDetails_m.js         # Scehma / Model for create events Deatils 
    ├── bookedEvents_m.js         # Scehma / Model for Bokked Events 
├── routes/                       
│   └── userRoutes.js             # Main routing file
├── package.json                  # Project packages
├──                       
└── README.md                     # This file (project documentation)



############################################################################  ROUTS MANAGEMENT  ###########################################################################################################################################################################################################



    | Api for   |  Routes |            url                                 |     PURPOSE             |        Description                                          
    |---------- |----------|-----------------------------------------------|-------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
    |   USER    |   POST   | localhost:3000/api/register                   | FOR REGSITER USER       |  API FOR REGSITER THE USER  [ WITH JWT TOKEN , ID AND ROLE I M SAVE IN TOKEN ]     |
    |---------- |----------|-----------------------------------------------|-------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
    |   USER    |   POST   | localhost:3000/api/login                      | FOR LOGIN USER          |  API FOR LOGIN THE USER   [ AFTRE LOGIN  , ID AND ROLE I M SAVE IN TOKEN ]         |                                                         |
    |---------- |----------|-----------------------------------------------|-------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
    |  USER     |  GET     | localhost:3000/api/events                     |  GET ALL EVENTS         |   GET ALL EVENTS FROM EVENTS Scehma AND MODEL                                      |                        
    |---------- |----------|-----------------------------------------------|-------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
    |  USER     |  POST    | localhost:1000/api/eventsdetails/:eventid     | GET EVENT DETAILS       |                                                                                    |
    |---------- |----------|-----------------------------------------------|-------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
    |  USER     |  GET     | localhost:1000/api/eventbooking/:eventid      | EVENT BOOKED            |  USER SAVE OUR BOKKING                                                             |                                              |
    ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

                                                                            #  ORGANIZER ROUTES  #

    |..........................................................................................................................................................................|
    | ORGANIZER |  POST    | localhost:1000/api/addevents                  | ADD EVENTS              |  ORGANIZER ADD THE EVENTS                                               |
    |---------- |----------|-----------------------------------------------|-------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|
    | ORGANIZER |  POST    | localhost:1000/api/addeventsdetails/:eventid  | ADD EVENT DETAILS       |  ORGANIZER ADD THE EVENTSDETAILS BASE ON EVENT ID                       |                                                                                  |
    |---------- |----------|-----------------------------------------------|-------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|
    | ORGANIZER |  PUT     | localhost:3000/api/editevents/:id             | UPDATE EVENT            |  ORGANIZER UPDATE EVENTS                                                |
    |---------- |----------|-----------------------------------------------|-------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|
    | ORGANIZER |  DELETE  | localhost:3000/api/eventdelete/:id            | DELETE EVENT            |   ORGANIZER DELETE EVENTS WITH THE HELP OF EVENT ID                     |                                                                                     |
    |---------- |----------|-----------------------------------------------|-------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|
    | ORGANIZER |  GET     | localhost:3000/api/eventsattendance/:eventId  | GET ATTENDANCE          | ORGANIZER GET ATTENDANCE BASE ON EVENTID  , IF THEY LOGIN               |
    |---------- |----------|-----------------------------------------------|-------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|
   








